Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.07,Default,Man,0,0,0,,{\blur0}Bắt tay vào làm việc nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:51.83,Default,All,0,0,0,,{\blur0}Được.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.04,Default,Man,0,0,0,,{\blur0}A, Okazaki-kun.
