Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:21:59.50,Default,Yos,0,0,0,,{\blur0}Okazaki, nhanh lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:00.92,Default,Oka,0,0,0,,{\blur0}V-Vâng!
